{"tid":804621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：鋼盤墊電磁爐底 中年婦被轟冇腦反致謝","createTime":"2018-09-03T07:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T07:01:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"193eebefad3912c2f69294e1d4277a12726b69d2","tid":804621,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PAFB3QgTork_8SCvjnsAkw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-09-02/47d2f680-af07-11e8-afd2-e11d48f69dd2_bkn-20180902193702853-0902_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPAFB3QgTork_8SCvjnsAkw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-09-02%2F47d2f680-af07-11e8-afd2-e11d48f69dd2_bkn-20180902193702853-0902_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=b57d7502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=2udh5xhCYt10QHcWxQFnE8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e7dd9f32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】老一輩使用新產品時往往會鬧出不少笑話，小事固然無傷大雅，惟有些時候，錯誤使用隨時導致嚴重的家居意外...日前（31日），一名中年女士於網上「請教」如何正確使用電磁爐，發文附有一張相片，顯示她因錯誤使用，導致電磁爐底部嚴重熔化，有如「異形口水」。發文引來不少網民恥笑，惟該名女士不但沒有生氣，更虛心地向提供資訊的網民道謝，回應獲激讚。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士在Facebook群組「柴灣人柴灣事」發文，照片顯示電磁爐疑因被不銹鋼盤「墊高」，不能正常散熱，底部的膠殼熔化成漿糊狀。她指，當時有7個人在打邊爐，因此將電磁爐「墊高」以便各人進食，沒人認為做法不妥。眾人用餐後，收拾餐桌時才發現電磁爐底已熔化，部分熔掉的膠更與不銹鋼盤「相連」。她認真地詢問：「請問各位街坊，我用不銹鋼盤做底，是否用法不當？」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民直斥陳女士沒有常識，更罵其「冇腦」，又嘲諷她「唔識睇說明書？」不過面對負評，陳不但沒有生氣，更向一眾網民表示：「依家明白了，以後會謹記，感謝解答！」有人留言直指，沒有釀成火災，已是十分「大命」，陳亦回應謂：「我都覺得好好彩！」<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說：<br />\n<br />\nHeliy Mak：經一事長一智，最重要無嚴重意外、無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\nGary Tongk：上了寶貴一課，但也教識了所有柴灣人，你個爐犧牲得有價值，多謝晒！<br />\n<br />\n彭育成：不銹鋼盤都係金屬，應放膠板/木板。<br />\n<br />\nChin Wai Chan：你係咪想燒咗間屋？"},{"pid":"c943f50a87a5f168e0807378aa2173bd66a2640f","tid":804621,"uid":114483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起雞髀鍵盤底"},{"pid":"f185a43cd978ff770b3392ced331af5875d7c51d","tid":804621,"uid":31780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"唔臭架咩"},{"pid":"11555f7deae02277c1990322d04a4f4496ad7cf2","tid":804621,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f185a43cd978ff770b3392ced331af5875d7c51d","tid":804621,"uid":31780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"唔臭架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"可能個湯底陣味太濃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b1532e18709c23f723235cf6f3a176b12b28ff","tid":804621,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"電磁爐「墊高」散唔到熱 .. 我都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e7a0125f8827a36b9d8c4e1705f72b084089e5","tid":804621,"uid":201604,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"33b1532e18709c23f723235cf6f3a176b12b28ff","tid":804621,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"電磁爐「墊高」散唔到熱 .. 我都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"唔係散唔到熱 係電磁爐會整熱金屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25529c69b2df0fa10f10bc0dea301faf0808320","tid":804621,"uid":149361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"唔識有咩咁出奇  笑鳩人果d根本就係老屎fuc心理"},{"pid":"06faaa466cd59b55703d73592da731c036b12918","tid":804621,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25529c69b2df0fa10f10bc0dea301faf0808320","tid":804621,"uid":149361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"唔識有咩咁出奇  笑鳩人果d根本就係老屎fuc心理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"串完人 又唔解釋點解 我諗佢地